character.name: A smooth-coated miniture dachshund with a sleek black coat and warm tan markings on the face, chest, and paws. They’ve got that classic long body with short legs, floppy ears, and big, round, very expressive eyes looking straight up at the camera. The posture feels alert but gentle, like they’re patiently waiting for attention or a treat. Overall vibe: curious, sweet, and slightly pleading in the most dachshund way possible.
